Copa Renner

International tournament promoted by Tintas Renner, a painting company, that sponsored the clubs unvolved.
Palmares

1996 - Grêmio (Porto Alegre, Brazil)
1997 - Bahia (Salvador, Brazil)
1996

At Cidreira, RS, Brazil

Participants:
Grêmio (Porto Alegre, Brazil)
Sport (Recife, Brazil)
Nacional (Montevideo, Uruguay)
Cerro Porteño (Asunción, Paraguay)

Semifinals [Feb 16]
Grêmio      3-2 Nacional
Sport       2-0 Cerro Porteño

Third Place Match [Feb 17]
result unknown

Final [Feb 17]
Grêmio      2-2 Sport         [4-2 pen]
1997

At  Recife, PE, Brazil

Participants:
Bahia (Salvador, Brazil)
Sport (Recife, Brazil)
Cerro Porteño (Asunción, Paraguay)
Nacional (Montevideo, Uruguay)

